								
							***A N S I B L E***


pre-requisite:

 python

1st do this thing

	apt-get update && apt-get upgrade -y
	apt-get install ansible

check whether ansible is install or not

	ansible --version

check config & host file

	cd /etc/ansible

go to /etc/ansible/hosts  and put one or more remote systems in it

add host name or ip address on host file 

	vi hosts  
	eg. 192.0.2.50	OR
	aserver.example.org  OR
	bserver.example.org

Now ping all your nodes

	ansible all -m ping


